videos.description: Keenan Evans drives to the basket and throws it up for Zach Smith who throws down an acrobatic one-handed dunk for Texas Tech.
videos.headline: Evans sets up unreal dunk from Smith

videos.description: Brandone Francis kicks it out to Jarrett Culver who makes a long jumper to cut TCU's lead in the first half.
videos.headline: Culver knocks down long 3-pointer for TTU

videos.description: Texas Tech goes for their first lead of the game and Kenrich Williams blocks a shot from behind to keep TCU ahead.
videos.headline: Williams gets big block for TCU

videos.description: Keenan Evans draws contact as he drives to the basket and ties the game with the and-1 free throw.
videos.headline: Evans ties it up with tough and-1 layup

videos.description: Keenan Evans extends Texas Tech's lead and reaches 10 points in the second half as he draws contact on a quick layup.
videos.headline: Evans steals momentum with and-1 layup

videos.description: Zhaire Smith gets under the basket and throws up a reverse layup to extend Texas Tech's lead.
videos.headline: Smith makes impressive reverse layup for TTU
